<div class="content px-5">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4 header mt-3">Appointment Letter</h2>

  <p class="mt-5 mb-2"><strong>Date:</strong> <%= Date.today.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></p>

  <p><strong>To:</strong> <%= @document.user.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Position:</strong> HR Executive</p>
  <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Appointment Letter</p>

  <p class="mt-5 mb-2"><strong>Dear <%= @document.user.name %>,</strong></p>

  <p class="mt-5">
    Following your acceptance of the job offer, we are pleased to confirm your appointment
    with <strong>Technomatz IT Solutions Pvt. Ltd.</strong> as a <strong><%= @document.start_position %></strong>.
    Your employment is subject to the terms and conditions listed below:
  </p>

  <ul class="mt-3">
    <li><strong>Starting Date:</strong> <%= @document.start_date.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></li>
    <li><strong>Work Timings:</strong> Flexible, with 8 hours of active work from Monday to Friday.</li>
    <li><strong>Probation Period:</strong> Three months, after which employment becomes permanent.</li>
    <li><strong>Service Agreement:</strong> Minimum association period of one year.</li>
    <li><strong>Salary (CTC):</strong> <%= @document.new_salary %></li>
    <li><strong>Annual Leave:</strong> 12 days of earned leave and 2 optional leave days per year.</li>
    <li><strong>Notice Period:</strong> 45 working days required for resignation, with possible extensions.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="lh-lg mt-4">
    If you have further questions, please contact me or approach the HR department directly.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-5">
    Congratulations on your appointment and welcome to Technomatz IT Solutions Pvt Ltd.
    We look forward to years of fruitful cooperation and success.
  </p>

  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-6">
      <p><strong>HR Department</strong></p>
      <p>Technomatz IT Solutions Pvt Ltd.</p>
      <p>____________________</p>
      <p>Name and signature</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 text-end">
      <p>____________________</p>
      <p>Name and signature</p>
      <p>Employee</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
